node.text: #FieldRoastPartner Handheld Happiness = @fieldroast Stadium Dogs with Chao Cheese Sauce, Potato Chips, & Creamy Avocado. Yes Please! This Creamy & Crunchy, Flavour-Packed, Garlicky Smoked Plant-Based Perfection was made with inspo from your amazing suggestions on my IG Story for the Field Roast Make Taste Happen Challenge. These Super Fun (and perfectly grillable) Hotdogs are Guaranteed to Please at the Cookout this Summer. Recipe On My Site Now. Thanks for submitting your fav ingredients y’all! Have the best day everyone! You’re awesome! #FieldRoast #MakeTasteHappen

node.text: #ad Weeknight Deliciousness = Spicy Red Lentil & Chorizo Soup with Crispy Fried Tortillas. Yes Please! One of my favourite soups ever! Beautiful @caciqueinc Pork Chorizo & Jalapeño-Kissed Spicy Red Lentil Soup finished with a Drizzle of Cacique Crema Mexicana & a Heaping Helping of Ranchero Queso Fresco. A Flavour Explosion! Recipe Link in Profile. Have a great day everyone. You’re Awesome! #GoAutentico

node.text: Hey friends! My friends at @harvesthouseatl need our help. They provide essential services to the homeless & hurting in our community, & the increasing shortage of food & supplies will affect the most vulnerable among us first. We can help ensure that these folks have access to nutritious, healthy, & delicious meals every day. Hit the link in my profile for more info and to help. Thanks y’all. #FoodNation #GoodFoodForAll
